Label: Dual Credit Courses in HS [hdc17]
Notes: hdc17: How many college courses for credit did you complete in HS?

Label: Transfer Credits at Entry [trnsfr_cr]
Notes: ttrnsfr_cr: About how many credits do you expect to transfer?

Label: FASt Status (Treatment X) [FASt vs non-FASt]
Equation: x_FASt = I(trnsfr_cr ≥ 12); paths: a1→M1, a2→M2, c'→Y

Label: Credit Dose (Moderator Z)
Notes: Units in 10-credit increments above 12; Z=0 for all non-FASt

Label: Credit Dose (Centered)
Equation: credit_dose_c = credit_dose − M̄; moderates a1, a2 paths
Notes: Mean-centered; used in XZ_c interaction term

Label: Treatment x Dose Interaction
Equation: XZ_c = X × Z_c; paths: a1z→M1, a2z→M2
Notes: First-stage moderation; a1z, a2z test dose-dependent mediation

Label: Developmental Adjustment
Equation: DevAdj =~ 1*Belong + λ*Gains + λ*SupportEnv + λ*Satisf; DevAdj ~ c'*X + b1*M1 + b2*M2

Label: I feel valued by this institution [SBvalued]
I feel like part of the community [SBcommunity]
Perceived Gains
Equation: Gains =~ pganalyze + pgthink + pgwork + pgvalues + pgprobsolve; DevAdj =~ λ*Gains
Notes: 1st-order: std.lv ID (all loadings free); 2nd-order: λ free

Label: Developing or clarifying personal code of values [pgvalues]
Supportive Environment
Equation: SupportEnv =~ SEacademic + SEwellness + SEnonacad + SEactivities + SEdiverse; DevAdj =~ λ*SupportEnv
Notes: 1st-order: std.lv ID (all loadings free); 2nd-order: λ free

Label: Providing support to help students succeed academically [SEacademic]
Encouraging contact among students from different backgrounds [SEdiverse]
Satisfaction
Notes: 1st-order: std.lv ID (all loadings free); 2nd-order: λ free

Label: Would go to same institution again [sameinst]
Emotional Distress
Equation: EmoDiss ~ a1*X + a1z*XZ + covariates; EmoDiss =~ MHWd*
Notes: Higher scores = more distress; structural: M1 regressed on X, XZ

Label: Quality of Engagement
Equation: QualEngag ~ a2*X + a2z*XZ + covariates; QualEngag =~ QI*
Notes: Quality of interactions; structural: M2 regressed on X, XZ

Label: Cohort Year [cohort]
Notes: Academic cohort year; also MG moderator

Label: High School Grades [hgrades23]
Notes: hgrades23: What were most of your high school grades?

Label: High School GPA (Centered)
Notes: Mean-centered version used in PS model

Label: AP Course Load (High) [hapcl13]
Notes: Derived from hapcl13: How many AP classes completed? Recoded 1=3+ courses

Label: Pre-Calculus/Trigonometry with C or better [hprecalc13]
Notes: hprecalc13: Earned C or better in Pre-Calculus or Trigonometry

Label: HS Courses Challenged You [hchallenge]
Notes: To what extent did your courses challenge you to do your best work?

Label: Expected: Talk career plans with faculty [cSFcareer]
Notes: How often do you expect to talk about career plans with a faculty member?

Label: First-Generation Status [bfirstgen]
Notes: bfirstgen: Neither parent/guardian holds bachelor's degree

Label: Living Situation [cliving18]
Notes: cliving18: Where will you be living while attending college?
